  "texts": [
    "A brief cover letter describing the aim of the study and an estimated completion time was sent, along with a consent form, to maximize response rates.",
    "In-depth semi-structured interviews were conducted face-to-face and by Zoom, based on participant preference and availability.",
    "Interviews took approximately 30-45 minutes each and were audio-recorded with the participant's consent.",
    "Responses from the survey were auto-collected and saved in a password-protected spreadsheet (Google Sheets or Excel).",
    "The interviews were recorded digitally and safely stored in an encrypted password-protected cloud drive asset and hand-transcribed for analysis."
  ],
